{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_53_03",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――九月二十六日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、やっぱり何かお手伝い出来ることは\nありませんか？　どうにも落ち着かなくて",
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clean-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11200.000000000002,
          "startTime": 17.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ。パーティの片付けは、ほとんど終わってるし\nあとは、このお皿を拭いちゃえば……はい、おしまい！",
      "startTime": 15.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日の日くらいは、のんびりしてていいのよ\n……ふふ、何か飲みましょうか。私も付き合うから",
      "startTime": 26.2843932759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、お仕事とプライベートは分けている\nつもりなんですが、家事はもう趣味みたいなもので",
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "日頃のルーティンもあるものね。気持ちは分かるわ\nでも、全部忘れて思いっきり羽を伸ばすのも大事よ",
      "startTime": 49.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。雑誌の企画では千紗や遙子さんのおかげで\n一杯好きなことをさせてもらえて本当に楽しかったです",
      "startTime": 59.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。たまには休んだり、誰かに甘えていいのよ\n周りも、沙季ちゃんに甘えてほしいって思ってるから",
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.33333329999,
          "startTime": 76.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6966.666666599991,
          "startTime": 77.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ほら。なでなで～",
      "startTime": 74.4666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……！？　く、くすぐったいです……\nうぅ、これは甘やかされてるのとは少し違うような……",
      "startTime": 82.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、じゃあ……\nこのお菓子、美味しいわよ。はい、あ～ん",
      "startTime": 93.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……！？　こ、こういうこと、千紗としか\nしたことないのに……。あ、あ～ん……あむ",
      "startTime": 101.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "美味しい？　ふふふ、私って一人っ子だから\n妹がほしかったのよね。沙季ちゃん、おいで～",
      "startTime": 112.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8233.33333330001,
          "startTime": 120.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "おいでって言われても……ひゃあ！？\nは、遙子さんから抱きついているじゃないですか！？",
      "startTime": 121.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "今日くらいは甘えてって言ったでしょ？\nいいから、遙子お姉ちゃんに甘えるの～！",
      "startTime": 128.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ……待って。この感じ……\n遙子さんが飲んでるのって、もしかして……",
      "startTime": 137.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "遙子、酔ってないも～ん！　ただぁ、可愛い妹ちゃんに\n甘えてほしいだけなの～。ね、お姉ちゃんって呼んで～",
      "startTime": 146.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12933.336130700012,
          "startTime": 153.800012207
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12500.028967899994,
          "startTime": 158.9666956346
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15166.685994399984,
          "startTime": 161.6333526611
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 22899.993896500007,
          "startTime": 169.3666605632
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "お、重いです、離して下さい……んしょっ……\nふぅ、やっと抜け出せた。もうっ、私は部屋に戻ります",
      "startTime": 161.6000193278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十分後",
      "startTime": 170.9333465576,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11199.986775699983,
          "startTime": 182.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "むにゃむにゃ……\n沙季ちゃあん……お誕生日おめでとぉ……",
      "startTime": 176.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12766.666666600002,
          "startTime": 189.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、やっぱり寝てる。ほら、毛布持ってきましたから\nまったくもう。仕方ないですね、遙子お姉ちゃんは",
      "startTime": 192.166675822,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7799.990844700005,
          "startTime": 199.9666666667
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}